{"tid":357286,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【申請學生資助問題】有紅簿仔記錄仲使唔使交月結單副本？","createTime":"2017-08-12T17:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T17:39:59.000Z","uid":10366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76b429da126ef61e5905ede3f23fd44cd0940c9f","tid":357286,"uid":10366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"學資處嗰網有時就寫：存褶及月結單副本<br />\n有時就寫：存褶/月結單副本<br />\n<br />\n咁其實如果我有存褶既副本 仲使唔使交月結單副本？ 定兩種副本都要交？ <br />\n<br />\n上網睇有人話只交存褶副本就ok 想問清楚d 今日又紅日問唔到學資處 想早d準備好d證明文件 有冇申請過既巴絲解答？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b555ba4f8b4a9d8d13ec00aa5e72e8d256ed25c","tid":357286,"uid":84298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:14:58.000Z","msg":"如果你係講緊Non-means-tested loan，咁淨係交紅薄仔就OK<br />\n利申：我淨印紅薄仔批左"},{"pid":"c06446e14f04ea900419be73ff4d6a292e8bb7e1","tid":357286,"uid":72571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"以往2次都淨係交紅簿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9207b7de77a33f1033dfeb9fe1ecf8e5269cd76","tid":357286,"uid":10366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你係講緊Non-means-tested loan，咁淨係交紅薄仔就OK<br />\n利申：我淨印紅薄仔批左</blockquote><br />\n我係申請 資助專上課程學生資助計劃 (TSFS)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5c3a4fbfd62573dc4553c83bc1de775923ad06","tid":357286,"uid":10366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以往2次都淨係交紅簿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打都係 資助專上課程學生資助計劃 (TSFS)？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7360b47abe24cd0b8f1ddad368b35b3d02302915","tid":357286,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:18:51.00